                    </div>
                    <span>If your looking for a book to teach you how to assemble a kit bike...this is it.  It doesn't offer much help for someone looking to build their own bike from the ground up.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Buyers digest!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
